long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Here is another new adventure game for you. You will discover how fast you are while playing this game. You will embark on an adrenaline-filled journey as you move towards the goal by overcoming the obstacles in front of you with the help of the mouse.

You can contact with us support@zillakgames.com and share your thoughts and problems
